## Code to Print the transaction data from a binary file

### To run :

1. First clone this repository by executing `git clone "https://github.com/akhilagrawal1001/Blocks_and_Chains_Assignments"`
2. Change the directory to `Blocks_and_Chains_Assignments/Assignment4`
3. Run the command `node main.js`

### Sample Input:
```Path of Binary Data file  : 5df76f0bcfdcc4c0494cf64e302168069f586b1e36188666cc5bbb7a78846f71.dat```
